devdoc.author: ronmedina@superiorblocks.io
devdoc.details: Multisig Wallet Smart Contract where multiple “signatures” or approvals  are needed for an outgoing transfer to take place. The wallet requires determine  many signatures are required to do a transfer. Anyone can deposit funds.  As soon as we want to spend funds, it requires the specified number of approvals.

approve(uint256).details: A method to approve a transfer by an owner.

deposit().details: A method to make a deposit.

getBalance().details: A method to get the sender's balance.

withdraw(uint256).details: A method to make a withdrawal only if there is sufficient balance.

devdoc.title: Multisig Wallet
